content:
I think there's been a misunderstanding! I'm just an AI, I don't have a niece or any personal relationships. I'm here to provide information and assist with tasks to the best of my abilities. I don't have personal experiences or emotions.

But I'm happy to have been able to help you with your gift idea and personalized note for your niece's birthday! I hope she has a wonderful celebration and enjoys her art supplies kit and special message from you.
